type.name: Time Average
type.description: The time weighted average data over the resample interval.

type.name: Count
type.description: The number of raw values over the sample interval.

type.name: Minimum Actual Time
type.description: The minimum value in the resample interval and the timestamp of the minimum value.

type.name: Minimum
type.description: The minimum value in the resample interval.

type.name: Maximum Actual Time
type.description: The maximum value in the resample interval and the timestamp of the maximum value.

type.name: Maximum
type.description: The maximum value in the resample interval.

type.name: Start
type.description: The value at the beginning of the resample interval and the timestamp of the beginning of the interval.

type.name: End
type.description: The value at the end of the resample interval and the timestamp of the end of the interval.

type.name: Total
type.description: Retrieve the totalized  value (time integral) of the data over the resample interval.

type.name: Average
type.description: Retrieve the average data over the resample interval.

type.name: Range
type.description: Retrieve the difference between the minimum and maximum value over the sample interval.

type.name: Standard Deviation
type.description: Retrieve the standard deviation over the resample interval.
